\section{Consensus Habitat Attempt without Elops
saurus}\label{consensus-habitat-attempt-without-elops-saurus}

The outlier seems to be Elops saurus. This is an attempt to run the PGLS
without Elops saurus to see if anything changes.

\begin{Shaded}
\begin{Highlighting}[]
\NormalTok{pglseditconsensus <-}\StringTok{ }\NormalTok{vertmeas.speciesconsensus }\OperatorTok{%>%}\StringTok{ }
